description: The Brawler is ranked 9th and is one of the feistiest wrestlers we have. She never gives up, she hates being fingered, and she hates losing. The amount of energy she brings to the mat is amazing. Vendetta is ranked 5th and kicks the Brawler’s ass. In fact, Vendetta is coming along very nicely and might be in running for the Season Three championship title. Vendetta’s leg work in this match is something to watch! Despite her best efforts, the brawler gets molested on the mat and fucked hard in RD 4.
title: The Brawler (0-1) Vendetta (3-2)
